{"tid":315210,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「威爾頓」榮休歡送儀式圖輯","createTime":"2017-07-09T23:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T01:32:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"029013a0304ad066ba3a552aad6f570f8ffa2a23","tid":315210,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T23:59:57.000Z","msg":"深受香港馬迷愛戴的名駒「威爾頓」經已退役，香港賽馬會今天在沙田馬場為該駒舉行榮休歡送儀式。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「威爾頓」簡歷</strong><br />\n父 / 母 &ndash; 外祖父\tHoly Roman Emperor / Summer Trysting (美) &ndash; Alleged (美)<br />\n出生日期 / 出生地\t17-3-2010 / 愛爾蘭<br />\n進口類別 / 進口年份 / 烙號\t自購馬 / 2012 / P270<br />\n馬齡 / 毛色 / 性別 \t7 歲棗色閹馬<br />\n馬主\t鄭強輝<br />\n練馬師\t約翰摩亞<br />\n香港賽績(冠-亞-季-總出賽次數) / 總獎金\t10-2-2-32 / 62,819,325港元<br />\n首次在港出賽日期\t16-6-2013<br />\n最後在港出賽日期\t28-5-2017<br />\n<br />\n主要成就：<br />\n&bull;\t2014及2015年獲得本身最高世界評分123分，在2015年世界馬匹年終排名並列第八位。<br />\n&bull;\t2013/14年度馬季榮膺香港馬王、最佳中距離馬與最受歡迎馬匹。<br />\n&bull;\t香港歷來獲得總獎金第五高的賽駒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主要勝仗<br />\n<br />\n馬季\t\t日期\t\t賽事<br />\n2013/2014\t16/2/2014\t香港經典盃 (香港一級賽，1800米)<br />\n\t\t16/3/2014\t寶馬香港打吡大賽 (香港一級賽，2000米)<br />\n\t\t27/4/2014\t愛彼女皇盃 (一級賽，2000米)<br />\n2014/2015\t14/12/2014\t浪琴表香港盃 (一級賽，2000米)<br />\n\t\t7/2/2015\t百週年紀念銀瓶 (香港三級賽，1800米)<br />\n\t\t1/3/2015\t花旗銀行香港金盃 (一級賽，2000米)<br />\n2015/2016\t28/2/2016\t花旗銀行香港金盃 (一級賽，2000米)<br />\n2016/2017\t23/10/2016\t東方表行55週年沙田錦標 (二級賽，1600米)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://corporate.hkjc.com/image/201707/imgnews_102770_l_101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.hkjc.com%2Fimage%2F201707%2Fimgnews_102770_l_101.jpg&h=e33a51aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「威爾頓」最後一次在沙田馬場馬匹亮相圈巡行，與廣大馬迷道別。<br />\n<img src=\"http://corporate.hkjc.com/image/201707/imgnews_102770_l_102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.hkjc.com%2Fimage%2F201707%2Fimgnews_102770_l_102.jpg&h=6db55649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「威爾頓」馬主鄭強輝致送「威爾頓」珍藏馬蹄鐵予馬會主席葉錫安博士。<br />\n<img src=\"http://corporate.hkjc.com/image/201707/imgnews_102770_l_103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.hkjc.com%2Fimage%2F201707%2Fimgnews_102770_l_103.jpg&h=a11f56d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬會主席葉錫安博士致送「威爾頓」的珍藏紀念相予「威爾頓」馬主鄭強輝。<br />\n<img src=\"http://corporate.hkjc.com/image/201707/imgnews_102770_l_104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.hkjc.com%2Fimage%2F201707%2Fimgnews_102770_l_104.jpg&h=abda5fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬會賽馬業務及營運執行總監祁立賢致送紀念綵帶予「威爾頓」的練馬師約翰摩亞。<br />\n<img src=\"http://corporate.hkjc.com/image/201707/imgnews_102770_l_105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.hkjc.com%2Fimage%2F201707%2Fimgnews_102770_l_105.jpg&h=67705f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬會主席葉錫安博士、馬會賽馬業務及營運執行總監祁立賢、馬會賽事規管及發展執行總監夏定安、馬主鄭強輝與家人及練馬師約翰摩亞，在榮休歡送儀式上合照。<br />\n<img src=\"http://corporate.hkjc.com/image/201707/imgnews_102770_l_106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.hkjc.com%2Fimage%2F201707%2Fimgnews_102770_l_106.jpg&h=e9ff58b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在歡送儀式上，一眾嘉賓與「威爾頓」合照。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2017-07/news_2017070901518.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fchinese%2Fcorporate%2Fracing_news_item.asp%3Fin_file%3D%2Fchinese%2Fnews%2F2017-07%2Fnews_2017070901518.html&d=FT5iXao0TO42acrCgIi6pxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=4d738475\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkjc.com/chinese/corporate/racing_news_item.asp?in_file=/chinese/news/2017-07/news_2017070901518.html</a>"},{"pid":"01b0476e43f89defa2d0ae516512bc01a72720e4","tid":315210,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T00:02:39.000Z","msg":"條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5360ab86c42d77004cd1fca7a0df549ba7176f","tid":315210,"uid":64525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T00:25:46.000Z","msg":"講un力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"549db25883eeef323ff7a797d55adfd630672c37","tid":315210,"uid":2211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T00:49:28.000Z","msg":"威仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c921c8aabbd27f527e01e0ad22a37f6df648ba2","tid":315210,"uid":652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T00:57:42.000Z","msg":"紀念相好似送禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb7a8e83f29757247be292b50a140b7b514c00c","tid":315210,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:00:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9696f63d2c3f9a2d28a6fd7f13487eb88637f29a","tid":315210,"uid":8767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:13:23.000Z","msg":"左一條女好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"437742c46988ecc0519f84a4e67cee57dc67c49c","tid":315210,"uid":50385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"光耀明明係有錢仔都要做記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個老豆仲要偷燒鵝食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bca69dae26f18243d382ef82ea169fd60b23e58b","tid":315210,"uid":19151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/10/093148_19b0923b62f255c1aae877d1e4333b17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F10%2F093148_19b0923b62f255c1aae877d1e4333b17.jpg&h=6cf7c1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n純撚到呢"},{"pid":"281f0033676d6557ea85b7d308611306733934de","tid":315210,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T01:32:55.000Z","msg":"女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"